            <title>[FLINK-12006] ZooKeeperHaServicesTest.testSimpleCloseAndCleanupAllData is unstable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-12006</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is the log from a failed Travis run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://travis-ci.org/apache/flink/jobs/510263371&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://travis-ci.org/apache/flink/jobs/510263371&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The relevant section is:&lt;/p&gt;
